1
00:00:03,660 --> 00:00:05,134
Ran, how could you do this to me!!

2
00:00:06,650 --> 00:00:10,843
You knew better than anyone how much this company means to me.

3
00:00:11,780 --> 00:00:13,185
And yet, you still…

4
00:00:17,900 --> 00:00:24,487
Have you never trusted me at all this whole time?

5
00:00:26,280 --> 00:00:27,025
Ran..

6
00:00:44,305 --> 00:00:46,310
It could never work between us.

7
00:00:47,470 --> 00:00:48,829
You know that, P’Chat.

8
00:00:52,170 --> 00:00:53,847
We’re siblings.

9
00:01:31,510 --> 00:01:32,414
Mom!!!

10
00:01:37,630 --> 00:01:38,458
I missed you so much!

11
00:01:38,480 --> 00:01:39,970
I haven't seen you since this morning.

12
00:01:40,410 --> 00:01:45,592
Alright, alright! You’re hugging me so tight I can’t even breathe.

13
00:01:46,830 --> 00:01:48,043
Oops sorry!

14
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:53,243
So, what’s up, sweetie?

15
00:01:54,090 --> 00:01:56,720
Oh! I have something to show you.

16
00:01:58,967 --> 00:02:00,181
What is it?

17
00:02:01,110 --> 00:02:02,363
Let’s see…

18
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:09,418
Wow!! A perfect score? You did it!

19
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:11,854
You’re so talented.

20
00:02:12,996 --> 00:02:16,087
Whose daughter is this? You’re the best!

21
00:02:16,123 --> 00:02:18,090
Well, I’m your daughter, so I have to be smart like you!

22
00:02:18,320 --> 00:02:19,934
Yeahhh

23
00:02:24,669 --> 00:02:25,840
Dad’s home!

24
00:02:33,110 --> 00:02:34,152
Honey,

25
00:02:37,374 --> 00:02:39,370
why are you back so early today?

26
00:02:39,425 --> 00:02:42,821
Oh... well, I finished up my work early today.

27
00:02:45,450 --> 00:02:48,770
Chat, don't you have something you wanted to show me?

28
00:02:49,750 --> 00:02:54,072
Dad, well... today, I have something to show you.

29
00:02:54,094 --> 00:02:55,018
Just a moment, sweetie.

30
00:02:56,250 --> 00:03:00,196
I actually have someone I’d like you and your mother to meet.

31
00:03:21,620 --> 00:03:22,756
Hello.

32
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:25,069
- Yes
- This is Ranya.

33
00:03:25,112 --> 00:03:27,070
She’s the niece of one of my housemaids.

34
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:29,570
Her aunt passed away by sickness, and the girl has no other relatives left.

35
00:03:29,600 --> 00:03:32,654
I felt sorry for her, so I brought her here to ask for your permission

36
00:03:33,750 --> 00:03:36,720
A niece? Which housemaid's niece?

37
00:03:38,530 --> 00:03:39,825
You have never met her.

38
00:03:50,020 --> 00:03:55,032
If you don't mind, what do you think about having Ranya come stay as a playmate for our child?

39
00:03:57,480 --> 00:04:00,625
Little girl... is your name Ranya?

40
00:04:01,410 --> 00:04:05,738
Yes... uh, yes, madam.

41
00:04:07,020 --> 00:04:08,407
You can just call me "Auntie," dear.

42
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:13,047
Oh, but...

43
00:04:13,510 --> 00:04:18,254
In that case, you can stay here and be a playmate for Chat.

44
00:04:18,305 --> 00:04:20,829
And when you’re older, if you don't want to go anywhere else

45
00:04:20,887 --> 00:04:23,541
and want to work for me, I wouldn't mind at all.

46
00:04:25,540 --> 00:04:27,840
Thank you so much, Auntie.

47
00:04:28,730 --> 00:04:29,869
Thank you, sweetie.

48
00:04:30,870 --> 00:04:31,389
Yes.

49
00:04:32,872 --> 00:04:35,390
Chat, take care of your sister for me, okay?

50
00:04:38,100 --> 00:04:39,680
Would you like to walk around and see the house?

51
00:04:39,709 --> 00:04:41,076
I'll have Chat show you around.

52
00:04:42,570 --> 00:04:43,432
Yes, please.

53
00:04:44,500 --> 00:04:45,876
I’m busy.

54
00:04:45,905 --> 00:04:47,178
I have homework to do.

55
00:04:49,180 --> 00:04:50,298
Pimchat!

56
00:05:18,050 --> 00:05:21,163
Chat, why are you acting like this?

57
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,650
Please be reasonable.

58
00:05:24,470 --> 00:05:26,225
I just don’t like the look of her.

59
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:28,996
Dad brought some random kid into this house, we don’t even know who she is.

60
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:32,240
She isn’t even a relative, but I see Dad taking such good care of her.

61
00:05:34,167 --> 00:05:36,058
Isn’t she coming here to be a servant?

62
00:05:37,450 --> 00:05:40,218
Chat, that wasn't very nice for you.

63
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:43,614
How could I  treat a child that small like a servant?

64
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:53,229
Chat, do you know why I agreed to let Ranya stay with us?

65
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:57,861
It’s so that if the day comes when I’m no longer here,

66
00:05:59,280 --> 00:06:01,447
Ranya will be there to be your friend.

67
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:05,120
I can’t have any more children...

68
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:09,854
but if someone can be like a sister to you,

69
00:06:10,380 --> 00:06:11,810
It would make me very happy.

70
00:06:14,410 --> 00:06:17,847
Mom! Don’t talk like that.

71
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:22,334
Once I graduate, I’m going to take our company to a global level.

72
00:06:23,880 --> 00:06:25,425
Oh, is that so?

73
00:06:25,454 --> 00:06:26,378
Hmm...

74
00:06:27,080 --> 00:06:30,530
Mom, we’re going to be on the cover of a magazine as the most talented mother-daughter duo in Thailand.

75
00:06:32,650 --> 00:06:34,218
I’ll be looking forward to that, dear.

76
00:06:36,440 --> 00:06:43,687
So, you have to stay with me for a long time. for many more decades, okay?

77
00:06:47,430 --> 00:06:48,661
I’ll be waiting for that day.

78
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,534
As for the situation with Ran...

79
00:06:56,640 --> 00:06:58,909
please try giving her a chance first.

80
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:01,970
Just do it for me, okay?

81
00:07:05,970 --> 00:07:07,236
I’ll try.

82
00:07:09,620 --> 00:07:10,669
That’s my girl.

83
00:07:19,985 --> 00:07:21,990
Fine. I'll do it for you, Mom.

84
00:07:38,490 --> 00:07:40,109
Why do you keep following me around?

85
00:07:40,429 --> 00:07:42,734
Um.. well, Ran...

86
00:07:46,340 --> 00:07:48,072
I just want to get close to you, Sis.

87
00:07:48,770 --> 00:07:51,192
Auntie told me to come and play with you.

88
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:59,003
I’m going to be straight with you,

89
00:07:59,740 --> 00:08:01,556
I have no interest in being your friend.

90
00:08:02,980 --> 00:08:05,803
Stop bothering me and just stay out of my way.

91
00:08:05,832 --> 00:08:07,447
But Ran just wanted to...

92
00:08:07,498 --> 00:08:08,152
Ugh!

93
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:11,345
I told you, you’re annoying!

94
00:08:12,840 --> 00:08:13,956
- Why are you so...
- Chat!

95
00:08:18,810 --> 00:08:20,523
Why do you talk to Ranya like that?

96
00:08:21,530 --> 00:08:23,040
It’s nothing, Uncle.

97
00:08:23,083 --> 00:08:25,418
She was just saying...

98
00:08:25,454 --> 00:08:26,610
What did you do to her?

99
00:08:28,550 --> 00:08:29,570
And if I did, so what?

100
00:08:30,430 --> 00:08:31,861
Since when did you ever care about me anyway?

101
00:08:32,690 --> 00:08:33,498
Chat!

102
00:08:42,261 --> 00:08:45,047
Come on, don't pay her any mind.

103
00:08:47,570 --> 00:08:48,290
Yes.

104
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,232
Wait, Chat!

105
00:09:24,590 --> 00:09:25,854
What does this mean, Dad?

106
00:09:27,272 --> 00:09:30,589
Come on, aren't you heading to school anyway?

107
00:09:30,970 --> 00:09:32,400
Just take Ranya with you.

108
00:09:34,820 --> 00:09:36,167
And does Mom know about this?

109
00:09:36,760 --> 00:09:38,305
Have you even asked her permission yet?

110
00:09:39,740 --> 00:09:40,996
Why should I have to ask?

111
00:09:47,430 --> 00:09:49,789
Since you’re all living in the same house now,

112
00:09:49,970 --> 00:09:52,669
just take your sister to school with you. Please honey,

113
00:09:54,880 --> 00:09:57,840
Um, about yesterday, I...

114
00:10:04,340 --> 00:10:06,472
Just do it, focus on your studies, okay?

115
00:10:12,170 --> 00:10:13,738
Don't act like we know each other.

116
00:10:13,767 --> 00:10:14,960
And if you see me, don't you dare say hello.

117
00:10:15,760 --> 00:10:16,414
Yes.

118
00:10:26,610 --> 00:10:30,160
I told you not to follow me! Don't you understand?

119
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:32,785
Give me some space.

120
00:10:41,300 --> 00:10:41,883
Huh?

121
00:10:43,550 --> 00:10:46,661
So your dad brought this kid to study here?

122
00:10:47,600 --> 00:10:48,501
Yeah, he did.

123
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:50,516
But why?

124
00:10:51,160 --> 00:10:52,821
She’s just the niece of some old servant.

125
00:10:53,530 --> 00:10:54,618
What's the big deal?

126
00:10:56,780 --> 00:10:58,218
How should I know?

127
00:11:03,100 --> 00:11:04,378
You want me to handle this for you?

128
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:08,145
What are you going to do?

129
00:11:39,640 --> 00:11:41,163
Is something wrong?

130
00:11:42,170 --> 00:11:43,585
You’re Ranya, right?

131
00:11:44,170 --> 00:11:44,727
Yeah.
